{"word":"G2146 - εὐπροσωπέω - euprosōpéō - yoo-pros-o-peh'-o - Make a fair show","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐπροσωπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">euprosōpéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-pros-o-peh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make a fair show</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நல்வேஷம்"},{"paragraph":"to make a fair show; to please"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G4383 - πρόσωπον - prósōpon - pros'-o-pon/4383\">G4383</a>; to <i>be of good countenance</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>make a display:</i> - make a fair show.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2146/2146\">G2146</a>, <a href=\"#/G4380/4380\">G4380</a>, <a href=\"#/G4381/4381\">G4381</a>, <a href=\"#/G4382/4382\">G4382</a>, <a href=\"#/G4383/4383\">G4383</a>, <a href=\"#/G678/678\">G678</a>"}]}